        "text": "Pattern Languages are tools for sense-making and purpose driven design. Their purpose is (meeting our need for) wholeness and enlivenment. Each pattern of a Pattern language allows us to semi-formalize and communicate both expert and tacit knowledge within a specific domain of practice. \n"
